# Whitelist approach: the root build context is ~1.7GB (TuzkaOCR, venvs, bench,
# test-data). Ignore everything, then re-include only what the api/worker images
# actually need, so `docker build` ships a tiny context.
*

!app
!alembic
!alembic.ini
!pyproject.toml

# Re-excludes inside the whitelisted dirs.
**/__pycache__
**/*.py[cod]
